BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Emerson Theatres": "https://emersontheatres.org/event/sweet-charity/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:emerson_theatres
X-SOURCE:Emerson Theatres
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260416T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T235959
DTSTAMP:20260324T222034
CREATED:20250905T193939Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251031T143736Z
UID:10000040-1776297600-1776556799@emersontheatres.org
SUMMARY:SWEET CHARITY
DESCRIPTION:SWEET CHARITY\n\n\n\nBook by Neil SimonMusic by Cy ColemanLyrics by Dorothy FieldsDirected & Choreographed by Larry SousaMusic Direction by Jonathan Goldberg\n\n\n\n\nThe story of Charity Hope Valentine\, a dance hall hostess in NYC\, who is optimistic and always searching for love despite a string of bad relationships. The musical follws her misadventures as she encounters various men\, including a famous move star and a shy accountant\, ultimately grappling with her hopes and disappointments in love. \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nSWEET CHARITY is presented by special arrangement with Concord Theatricals on behalf of Tams Witmark\, LLC.  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDates\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nEvent Info\n\n\n\nVenue\n\n\n\n\n\nDetails\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n2 hours 30 mins \n\n\n\nincluding a 15 min intermission \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAges 14+ \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nContent Warning: \n\n\n\nMature themes such as alcohol use\, smoking\, sexual references & themes including sex work and sexually suggestive humor. \n\n\n\n\n\nHealth & Safety Information
URL:https://emersontheatres.org/event/sweet-charity/
LOCATION:Emerson Cutler Majestic Theatre\, 219 Tremont St\, Boston\, MA\, 02116\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://emersontheatres.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/81/2025/09/CharityThumb.png
END:VEVENT
