SUMMARY:The Secret Sharer
DESCRIPTION:In this world premiere performance\, Joseph Conrad’s acclaimed novella is adapted to tell a powerful tale of two men\, outsiders in their societies\, who forge a shared\, intimate\, and healing connection against all odds.
